name: Bird Momma - GoGodotJam
description:
Feed your chicks so they can grow healthy!
If you will be too slow they will starve :(
Use your left mouse button to aim and fly to the cursor.
You can only pick up 1 worm at a time.
You feed the chicks by just flying near them.

Unfortunately I didn't have time for any sound :/
Made with
Godot 3.3.2
Krita
Time spent in total < 20h
